{"type": "article", "id": 28051, "title": "沙滩躺椅", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-12T06:57:12Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 14, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702125448BFEtIyoeRNPfShqD.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>想在沙滩上慵懒地吹吹风、看看海？Alite 推出的这款名为 Meadow 的躺椅正是为此而设计的。躺椅采用了热塑性弹性体（TPE）材料，具有橡胶的高回弹性，与铝制框架的搭配可以让你非常安心地躺在上面度过一段舒适懒散的时光。它可以卷起之后打包存放，需要的时候还能作为枕头使用，重量约为 839 克，便于随身携带。这是它的<a href=\"https://alitedesigns.com/collections/shop-all/products/meadow-rest\">购买链接</a>，售价为 64.99 美元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125446hrtK3MsTFDZ8aHUc.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125446rKtRpsnzm4TNlyvU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070212544759XdDjy1PBn6Ikwb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125447k6CyQ2f3BrpTjqPz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}